TT:  They called for cat bots, but I just came here
because I was more likely to find a scanner here to
detect my brother when he arrives than build one from
the rubble of that Maximal base back there.

Meanwhile Legacy crosses through India.

> The panther silently crept up the last few feet to
> the group of 
> signatures, having recognized one he had met

> flashed as a feline grin passed over his muzzle as

> the under brush behind the bot.

> some sort of 
> invitation to this location?" He spoke, his voice
> slow and soft not 
> to startle the rather volatile bot.
